    narr:StyleObs_DirectSpeechPlaybook
      a narr:StyleObservation ;
      skos:broader narr:SpeakerIdiolects ;
      dct:source narr:Sample_CustomerArchitectSponsorNotChampion_20260421 ;
      skos:note "Tony's quoted speech is directive and filler-heavy ('Right. Right. Blah, blah, blah.') — a characteristic idiolect that signals informal authority. The playbook steps are dictated verbatim in Tony's voice, giving the document a transcript-as-prescription register. Scarlet's speech is more analytical and self-diagnostic." ;
